  "final_answer": "Heena is believed to help cure leg pain due to its various chemical compounds. The key compounds in Heena include copper, glucose, and other substances like methanol, sodium, and ethanol. According to Hazrat Salma Umme Rafe’, Rasoolullah advised using Heena for leg pain. It is essential to note that while these compounds may be present in Heena, their effectiveness in treating leg pain is not definitively proven and may vary from person to person. \n\nPlease consult a healthcare professional before using Heena or any other ingredient for medicinal purposes, as the information provided is for general knowledge only and may not be suitable for individual use. A healthcare professional can provide personalized advice and help you make informed decisions about your health.",
